headline.main: NYPD: No Evidence of Vandalism at Largely Jewish Cemetery
headline.print_headline: NYPD: No Evidence of Vandalism at Largely Jewish Cemetery

lead_paragraph: The New York Police Department says no evidence of vandalism has been found at a predominantly Jewish cemetery where more than 40 tombstones were toppled over.
